Numpy 2.0 auto-restart fix applied to installation cells
Date: 2026-02-04
Affected notebooks: See commit message

All installation cells now include:
- Automatic runtime restart after pip install
- This prevents numpy binary incompatibility errors
- Users see message and runtime restarts automatically
- After restart, users skip installation cell and continue

Fixed notebooks:
- 03_atomic_visualization_showcase.ipynb
- 02_quantum_advantage_benchmark.ipynb  
- 01_getting_started.ipynb
- colab_quickstart.ipynb
- complete_benchmark.ipynb
- All others with similar pattern
